OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773302722
OL,3,CNorth Korean leader Kim Jong Un
OL,4,Cwatches cruise missile tests with his
OL,5,Cdaughter
OL,7,FNorth Korean leader Kim Jong Un and
OL,8,Fhis teenage daughter observed tests of
OL,9,Fstrategic cruise missiles fired from a
OL,10,Fwarship, state media reported on
OL,11,FWednesday.
OL,13,FThe images came as North Korea
OL,14,Fthreatened responses to US and South
OL,15,FKorean military drills as Washington
OL,16,Fcontinues its war with Israel on Iran.
OL,18,FThey show the two in a conference room
OL,19,Flooking at a screen showing weapons
OL,20,Fbeing fired from the Choe Hyon, a year-
OL,21,Fold naval destroyer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
