OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773302722
OL,3,CNorth Korean leader Kim Jong Un
OL,4,Cwatches cruise missile tests with his
OL,5,Cdaughter
OL,7,FKim Jong Un watched the missile
OL,8,Flaunches via video on Tuesday and
OL,9,Funderscored the need to maintain "a
OL,10,Fpowerful and reliable nuclear war
OL,11,Fdeterrent," the state media channel
OL,12,FKCNA reported.
OL,14,FThe girl, reportedly named Kim Ju Ae
OL,15,Fand about 13, has accompanied her
OL,16,Ffather at numerous prominent events,
OL,17,Fincluding military parades and weapons
OL,18,Flaunches, since late 2022.
