OL,3,CNorth Korean leader Kim Jong Un
OL,4,Cwatches cruise missile tests with his
OL,5,Cdaughter
OL,7,FIt quoted Kim Jong Un as saying the
OL,8,Flaunches were meant to demonstrate the
OL,9,Fnavy's strategic offensive posture and
OL,10,Fget troops familiarised with the
OL,11,Fweapons.
OL,13,FKim Jong Un observed similar cruise
OL,14,Fmissile launches from the Choe Hyon in
OL,15,Fperson last week, but his daughter was
OL,16,Fnot seen at that appearance.
