OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773302722
OL,3,CNorth Korean leader Kim Jong Un
OL,4,Cwatches cruise missile tests with his
OL,5,Cdaughter
OL,7,FTuesday's missile firings came after
OL,8,Fthe start of the springtime US and
OL,9,FSouth Korean military drills that
OL,10,FNorth Korea views as an invasion
OL,11,Frehearsal.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, Kim Jong Un's sister and
OL,14,Fsenior official, Kim Yo Jong, warned
OL,15,Fthe drills reveal the US and South
OL,16,FKorea's "inveterate repugnancy toward"
OL,17,FNorth Korea. She said North Korea will
OL,18,F"convince the enemies of our war
OL,19,Fdeterrence".
