OL,3,CNorth Korean leader Kim Jong Un
OL,4,Cwatches cruise missile tests with his
OL,5,Cdaughter
OL,7,FThe 11-day Freedom Shield drill that
OL,8,Fbegan Monday is largely a computer-
OL,9,Fsimulated command post exercise and
OL,10,Fwill be accompanied by a field
OL,11,Ftraining program. North Korea often
OL,12,Freacts to the two sets of training
OL,13,Fwith its own weapons tests.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
